@startuml
title UML state machine diagram

state ServiceCenterHome
ServiceCenterHome : entry / Logged in Service Center
ServiceCenterHome : do / Display home page
ServiceCenterHome : exit / Enter Damaged parts list
ServiceCenterHome : exit / Expiry Notification page
ServiceCenterHome : exit / Updating Information list

state ExpiryNotification
ExpiryNotification : entry / To view expiry notification
ExpiryNotification : do / Send service request to Car owner
ExpiryNotification : exit / Return to Service center home page

state Entering Damaged parts list
Entering Damaged parts list : entry / To enter Damaged parts list
Entering Damaged parts list : do / Preparing and entering damaged parts list
Entering Damaged parts list : exit / Return to service center home page

state Updating parts Information
Updating parts Information : entry / To update changed parts information
Updating parts Information : do / Update Information
Updating parts Information : exit / Return to Service center home page

state Logout
Logout : entry / To Logout
Logout : do / Logout
Logout : exit / Logged out Successfully
@enduml
